}}

游戏是日本的畅销作<ref>[[Dengeki_PlayStation|Dengeki PlayStation]] sales chart, January 2000, published in [[Official_UK_PlayStation_Magazine|Official UK PlayStation Magazine]] issue 54</ref>。本作最初的超级任天堂版本在開賣2个月内於日本售出200萬份<ref name="nppreview2">{{Cite journal| volume=73 |date=June 1995 |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |title=Chrono Trigger: A New Standard for RPGs | pages= 36}}</ref>。截至2003年，超级任天堂和PlayStation版累计在日本出货236万份，日本以外29万份<ref name="square-sales">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200402090000-01.pdf#page=27 |title=February 2, 2004 - February 4, 2004 |date=2004-02-09 |accessdate=2008-11-30 |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |page=27 |format=PDF |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213144948/http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200402090000-01.pdf#page=27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2006年，超级任天堂版累計已售出250万份<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.jp.playstation.com/software/title/slpm87395.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-25 |archive-date=2021-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125033057/https://www.jp.playstation.com/software/title/slpm87395.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[Famicom通信|Famicom通信]]》的首个读者交叉评论为游戏打出8/10<ref>読者 クロスレビュー: クロノ・トリガー. Weekly Famicom Tsūshin. No.332. Pg.32. 28 April 1995.</ref>，之后的交叉评论打出了9/10<ref>読者 クロスレビュー: クロノ・トリガー. Weekly Famicom Tsūshin. No.335. Pg.30. 12–19 May 1995.</ref>，游戏是1995年日本年度第三畅销游戏，仅位列《[[勇者斗恶龙VI_幻之大地|勇者斗恶龙VI 幻之大地]]》和《[[超级大金刚2_迪克西&迪迪|超级大金刚2 迪克西&迪迪]]》之后<ref name="1995 sales">{{cite web |url=http://gameranking.jp/ranking-sale/?0+1995 |title=販売本数ランキング |publisher=ゲームランキング |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510072555/http://gameranking.jp/ranking-sale/?0+1995 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏在北美一经发售也获得相当的成功，收录PlayStation版的合辑《最终幻想编年史》占据[[NPD集团|NPD]] TRSTS PlayStation销量榜首位达六周<ref name="gamerankings">{{cite web | editor=Game Rankings staff | title=Chrono Trigger Reviews | url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/563538.asp | publisher=[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]] | accessdate=2006-05-07 | archive-date=2006-05-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060519045221/http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/563538.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ign-review">{{cite web | date=2001-07-04 | author=IGN staff | title=IGN: Final Fantasy Chronicles Review | url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/166/166322p1.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2006-05-07 | archive-date=2011-08-03 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60eLEcdUY?url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/166/166322p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FFC-Sales">{{cite web | date=2001-08-15 | last=Wollenschlaeger | first=Alex | title=Final Fantasy Chronicles Tops Sales Charts Six Weeks in a Row | url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2001/081501d.html | publisher=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]] | accessdate=2006-05-08 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5w3JNIQry?url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2001/081501d.html | archive-date=2011-01-27 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。该版本作为索尼[[Greatest_Hit|Greatest Hit]]系列2003年的一款游戏发行。截至2009年3月，任天堂DS版的銷量為日本49万套，北美24万套，欧洲6万套<ref name="square-sales-ds">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090525_01en.pdf#page=7 |title=Results Briefing Session for the Fiscal Year ended March 31, 2009 |date=2009-05-25 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |page=28 |format=PDF |archive-date=2011-08-14 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60vD2utTG?url=http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090525_01en.pdf#page=7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2018年，在未含同年首度上市的PC版本下，本作累計已出貨超過350萬套<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.4gamer.net/games/411/G041119/20180228002/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-25 |archive-date=2021-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124213543/https://www.4gamer.net/games/411/G041119/20180228002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《时空之轮》获得大量來自媒體的好評。1995年《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》称其为史克威尔“史上最佳游戏”，称赞其改进的图形、音效和游戏性超越过往RPG作品<ref name="npreview1">{{Cite journal |date=July 1995 |volume=74 |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |title=Epic Center: Chrono Trigger |pages=52}}</ref>。《时空之轮》获得《电子游戏月刊》1995年电子游戏奖的数枚奖项，包括最佳角色扮演游戏、最佳卡带游戏音乐，以及最佳超级任天堂游戏奖<ref name="egmbuyersguide1996">{{cite journal |last= |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |year=1996 |month= |title=Electronic Gaming Monthly's Buyer's Guide |journal= |volume= |issue= |pages= |url=}}</ref>。2001年《[[官方美国PlayStation杂志|官方美国PlayStation杂志]]》称《时空之轮》“新颖且及其迷人”，并赞扬了游戏图形、音效和尤为令人印象深刻的故事<ref name="loadtime">{{Cite journal |date=August 2001 | editor=Sam Kennedy | journal=[[Official_U.S._PlayStation_Magazine|Official U.S. PlayStation Magazine]] |issue=47 | pages= 107 | publisher=Ziff Davis Media Inc.}}</ref>。2001年IGN评论道“《时空之轮》可能充斥每款游戏机RPG能想到的陈词滥调，但游戏的处理方式令其脱颖而出”，迷人的“故事使其免于太世俗”，是“既往最佳的电子游戏原声之一”<ref name="ign-review" />。其他评论批评游戏过短且在同时代作品中难度太低<ref name="FFC-Sales" /><ref name="playtime2">{{cite web | date=2001-10-30 | author=Bahamut | title=RPGFan Reviews - Chrono Trigger | url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/chronotrigger/Chrono_Trigger-6.html | publisher=RPGFan | accessdate=2006-07-22 | archive-date=2006-03-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060329192445/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/chronotrigger/Chrono_Trigger-6.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]的维多利亚·厄尔对游戏设计平衡性表示称赞，“开发者通过仔细设计的结构和模块化叙述方法，掌控了玩家自由”<ref>{{cite web|last=Earl|first=Victoria|title=Chrono Trigger's Design Secrets|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/172993/chrono_triggers_design_secrets.php|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|accessdate=2012-07-01|date=2012-06-26|archive-date=2012-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120629034715/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/172993/Chrono_Triggers_Design_Secrets.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

总体而言，评论称赞《时空之轮》“奇妙却不过分复杂的”故事、简单却革新的游戏性，以及多重结局带来的高重玩价值。原版《时空之轮》是得分汇总网站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]上排名第二的超级任天堂RPG<ref name="kotaku_rpgs">{{cite web |first=Mike |last=Fahey |url=http://kotaku.com/5546807/a-visual-guide-to-the-role+playing-game |title=A Visual Guide To The Role-Playing Game |publisher=Kotaku |date=2010-05-25 |accessdate=2010-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619204055/http://kotaku.com/5546807/a-visual-guide-to-the-role%20playing-game |archive-date=2010-06-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。吉尼斯世界纪录在2009年授予其电子游戏史上影响力第32大的游戏<ref>{{cite web | date=2009-02-26 | author=Brian Crecente | title=Super Mario Kart: Most Influential Video Game in History | url=http://kotaku.com/5160745/super-mario-kart-most-influential-video-game-in-history | publisher=Kotaku | accessdate=2009-02-27 | archive-date=2009-02-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090228050332/http://kotaku.com/5160745/super-mario-kart-most-influential-video-game-in-history | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》因《时空之轮》有十数个结局可供玩家探索，而称其为任天堂历史上最佳结尾之一<ref>{{cite book |title=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] 250th issue! |year=2010 |publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]] |location=[[South_San_Francisco,_California|South San Francisco, California]] |page=46 }}</ref>。[[汤姆·霍尔|汤姆·霍尔]]创作《[[星际之门|星际之门]]》时从《时空之轮》等游戏机游戏中汲取了灵感，并举篝火场景说明日式RPG的剧情深度<ref name="ngmpreview3">{{cite journal | date = May 1999 | journal = [[Next_Generation_Magazine|Next Generation Magazine]] | volume = 1 | issue = 53 | pages = 36–37 | title=Anachronox - The third leg in Ion Storm's triad may turned out to be its most underrated | publisher=Imagine Media}}</ref>。

《时空之轮》经常登上史上最佳电子游戏榜单。游戏在多媒体网站IGN的6次“史上100大游戏”榜单中皆居于高位——2002年第4名、2005年上半年第6位、2005年下半年第13位、2006年第2位、2007年第18位、2008年第2位<ref name="greatest-games">{{cite web | author=IGN staff | year=2006 | title=The Top 100 Games Ever | url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/001-010.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2007-08-08 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvLgRJE?url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/001-010.html | archive-date=2015-05-11 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="greatest-games2">{{cite web | author=IGN staff | year=2007 | title=The Top 100 Games Ever | url=http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_18.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2008-02-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071203032033/http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_18.html | archive-date=2007-12-03 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="greatest-games3">{{cite web | author=IGN staff | year=2008 | title=IGN Top 100 Games 2008 – 2 Chrono Trigger | url=http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_2.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2009-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090217225935/http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_2.html | archive-date=2009-02-17 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》在2001年最喜爱游戏榜单中将作品列为第15名，职员认为它是当时史克威尔制作最佳的非最终幻想作品<ref>{{cite web |title=Game Informer's Top 100 Games of All Time (Circa Issue 100) |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2009/11/16/game-informer-s-top-100-games-of-all-time-circa-issue-100.aspx |work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |last=Cork |first=Jeff |date=2009-11-16 |accessdate=2013-12-10 |archive-date=2016-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219152324/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2009/11/16/game-informer-s-top-100-games-of-all-time-circa-issue-100.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]将《时空之轮》列入2006年4月发布的“史上最佳游戏”榜单<ref name="gamespot-greatestgame">{{cite web | date=2006-04-17 | editor=GameSpot editorial team | title=The Greatest Games of All Time | url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgames/index.html | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060423115602/http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgames/index.html | archivedate=2006-04-23 | publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | accessdate=2006-05-06 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏还位列日本杂志《Fami通》2006年“史上最佳100”投票榜单的第28位<ref name="nextgen">{{cite web | author=Campbell, Colin | date=2006-03-03 | title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100 | url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | publisher=''Edge'' online | accessdate=2008-10-02 | archive-date=2008-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723051728/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《时空之轮》在2004年首次[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]电子游戏战中屈居《[[最终幻想VII|最终幻想VII]]》获得亚军。游戏在2008年[[电击Online|电击Online]]的史上最佳游戏读者投票中获得第8名<ref name="kotakudengeki">{{cite web | first=Brian | last=Ashcraft | date=2008-03-06 | title=Dengeki Readers Say Fav 2007 Game, Fav of All Time | url=http://kotaku.com/364353/dengeki-readers-say-fav-2007-game-fav-of-all-time | publisher=Kotaku | accessdate=2008-03-29 | archive-date=2008-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328132737/http://kotaku.com/364353/dengeki-readers-say-fav-2007-game-fav-of-all-time | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《任天堂力量》在20周年庆刊中称《时空之轮》是第5大超级任天堂游戏<ref name="np5best">{{Cite journal |date=August 2008 |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |volume=231 |title=Best of the Best | pages= 73 | publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]]}}</ref>。游戏位列2012年[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]“史上100大游戏”榜单的第2名<ref>{{cite web|title=The 100 best games of all time|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-games-ever/|publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|accessdate=2012-06-30|date=2012-04-20|archive-date=2016-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903202832/http://www.gamesradar.com/best-games-ever/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及“最佳JRPG”榜单的首位<ref>{{cite web|title=Best JRPGs|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-jrpgs/|publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|accessdate=2012-08-05|date=2012-07-19|archive-date=2013-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130122200149/http://www.gamesradar.com/best-jrpgs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。GamesRadar还成游戏是史上第2大超级任天堂游戏，仅次于《[[超级银河战士|超级银河战士]]》<ref>{{cite web | title=Best Super Nintendo games of all time | url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-snes-games-all-time/ | author=GamesRadar staff | publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] | date=2012-04-17 | accessdate=2013-02-25 | archive-date=2014-05-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502231234/http://www.gamesradar.com/best-snes-games-all-time/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==

=== 扩展 ===

《时空之轮》引发了数款相关发行作品；最早的是1995年7月31日发行的三款[[Satellaview|Satellaview]]作品<ref name="weeklyfamitsusatella">{{cite web | year=1995 | title=Weekly Famitsu | volume=347 | page=191 | url=http://superfamicom.org/blog/2013/07/dig-iii-chrono-trigger-bs-specials-naba-chan-and-more/ | accessdate=2013-07-28 | archive-date=2013-07-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729215428/http://superfamicom.org/blog/2013/07/dig-iii-chrono-trigger-bs-specials-naba-chan-and-more/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。它们为源自原版[[小游戏|小游戏]]的[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]《时空之轮 喷气摩托特别版》，记录游戏中角色和怪物的档案《时空之轮 角色博物馆》，以及收录游戏原声音乐的《时空之轮 音乐博物馆》。《角色博物馆》和《音乐博物馆》的内容还是PlayStation版《时空之轮》的附加内容。1996年7月31日的日本V-Jump节上，放映了[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]]制作的16分钟[[原创动画录像带|原创动画录像带]]（OVA）《[[时空冒险Numa_Monjar～|时空冒险Numa Monjar～]]》<ref>{{cite web |title=時空冒険ぬうまもんじゃ～ |url=http://www.production-ig.co.jp/contents/works_sp/0330_/index.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5w3JUJAai?url=http://www.production-ig.co.jp/contents/works_sp/0330_/index.html |archivedate=2011-01-27 |author=Production I.G staff |publisher=[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]] |language=ja |accessdate=2007-05-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Dimensional Adventure Numa Monjar |url=http://www.production-ig.com/contents/works/07_/000133.html |author=Production I.G staff |publisher=[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]] |accessdate=2007-05-20 |archive-date=2007-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070919215915/http://www.production-ig.com/contents/works/07_/000133.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 爱好者游戏 ===

有两款非官方尝试将部分游戏以[[三维计算机图形|3D图形]]引擎[[电子游戏重制|重制]]到PC的爱好者游戏——尝试重制《时空之轮》10个小互动过场的《时空复兴》（{{lang|en|''Chrono Resurrection''}}），以及尝试重制整款游戏<ref name="resurrection">{{cite web | date=2004-09-06 | author=Chrono Trigger: Resurrection staff | title=Project discontinued | url=http://www.opcoder.com/projects/chrono/ | publisher=Chrono Trigger: Resurrection | accessdate=2006-05-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060507142747/http://www.opcoder.com/projects/chrono/ | archive-date=2006-05-07 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="remake">{{cite web | author=Chrono Trigger Remake Project staff | title=CTRP Closes its doors | url=http://www.chrono-trigger.com/ | publisher=Chrono Trigger Remake Project | accessdate=2006-05-07 | archive-date=2006-05-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060503221829/http://www.chrono-trigger.com/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但被史克威尔下[[停止并终止|禁止令]]而强行停止的《时空之轮重制计划》<ref>{{Cite book | year=2004 | author=Jones, Darran | title=games October 2004; issue 24 | publisher=Highbury Publishing | page=130}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | year=2005 | author=Baker, Chris | title=Electronic Gaming Monthly February, 2005 | publisher=Ziff Davis Media}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | date=2006-03-20 | author=Ragan, Jess | title=Singin' the Brews: The History and Philosophy of Homebrew Game Development | url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=6&cId=3148820 | publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | accessdate=2006-11-09 | archive-date=2012-06-29 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20120629135142/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=6&cId=3148820 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | date=2006-04-17 | author=Shoemaker, Brad | title=The Greatest Games of All Time: Chrono Trigger | url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6147770/index.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2006-11-09 | archive-date=2011-08-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830220701/http://www.gamespot.com/features/6147770/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一个爱好者组织通过《时空之轮》[[ROM_hack|ROM破解]]创作后传《时空之轮：深红回声》（{{lang|en|''Chrono Trigger: Crimson Echoes''}}）；游戏从2004年开发到2009年；这款长篇游戏虽已实质完成，却同样在2009年5月发布前收到禁止函。函中还禁止散布既存的《时空之轮》ROM破解和文件<ref>{{cite web | date=2009-05-09 | author=ZeaLitY | title=Crimson Echoes | url=http://crimsonechoes.com/ | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090610205718/http://crimsonechoes.com/ | archivedate=2009-06-10 | accessdate=2009-05-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在禁止函发布后，未完成版游戏于2009年5月泄出，因其处于早期阶段，故操作受限<ref name="Leak1">[https://web.archive.org/web/20090606053219/http://www.gossipgamers.com/chrono-fan-game-crimson-echoes-98-complete-leaked/ Chrono Fan Game: Crimson Echoes 98% Complete Leaked], Retrieved February 7, 2011.</ref>。更完整的ROM之后在2011年1月泄出，可以自始至终完成游戏<ref name="Leak2">[http://www.joystiq.com/2011/01/18/fan-made-chrono-trigger-sequel-finds-release/ Fan-made Chrono Trigger sequel finds release] {{Wayback|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2011/01/18/fan-made-chrono-trigger-sequel-finds-release/ |date=20150131112645 }}, Retrieved February 7, 2011.</ref>。<!-- 中国大陆的深圳南晶科技公司将游戏“逆复刻”到[[FC|FC]]平台{{citation needed|time=2014-08-03T15:28:02+00:00}}。 -->

=== 续作 ===
{{main|时空系列}}

史克威尔在1996年发行了一套4个Satellaview游戏《[[Radical_Dreamers_-盗不走的宝石-|Radical Dreamers -盗不走的宝石-]]》。编剧加藤正人认为《时空之轮》以“未尽情节”完成，亲自编写并监督游戏<ref name="ultimania" />。游戏作为《时空之轮》的[[外传|外传]]，解析了前作的零散支线情节<ref name="weeklyfamitsu">{{cite web | year=1999 | title=Weekly Famitsu | url=http://www.chronocompendium.com/Term/Weekly_Famitsu.html | publisher=Chrono Compendium | accessdate=2006-07-03 | archive-date=2006-07-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060721173402/http://www.chronocompendium.com/Term/Weekly_Famitsu.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《盗不走的宝石》是短篇文字游戏，只配有少量图像与氛围音乐；游戏从未在日本以外官方发行。史克威尔计划将游戏作为彩蛋加入PlayStation版《时空之轮》，但加藤对其作品不满意并终止收入游戏<ref name="ultimania">{{cite book | year=1999 | editor=Studio BentStuff | title=Chrono Cross Ultimania | url=http://www.chronocompendium.com/Term/Ultimania_Developer_Interviews.html | pages=476–477 | language=ja | publisher=Square Enix | isbn=4-925075-73-X | access-date=2014-08-03 | archive-date=2009-04-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090418044713/http://www.chronocompendium.com/Term/Ultimania_Developer_Interviews.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

史克威尔1999年在索尼PlayStation平台发行了《[[穿越时空|穿越时空]]》。《穿越时空》是《时空之轮》的续作，使用了新设定和角色阵容<ref name="perfect-10">{{cite web | date=2000-01-06 | first=Andrew | last=Vestal | title=Chrono Cross Review | url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/chrono-cross-review/1900-2545933/ | publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | accessdate=2014-04-26 | archive-date=2013-12-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203083234/http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/chrono-cross-review/1900-2545933/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏使用[[平行世界|平行世界]]主题，被强行送入平行世界主角赛尔吉在原来的世界年幼时就已死亡。在神偷基德的帮助下，赛尔吉努力探寻他貌似死亡的真相，并获得了神秘遗物冻结之炎<ref name="perfect-10" />。编剧兼总监加藤正人将《穿越时空》看作“真正重做的《Radical Dreamers》”，《穿越时空》采用了《盗不走的宝石》中的某些主题、剧本、角色与设定<ref name="weeklyfamitsu" />。光田康典改编《盗不走的宝石》中的一些歌曲并为《穿越时空》配乐<ref name="crossost">{{cite web | date=2000-12-18 | title=Chrono Cross OST Liner Notes | url=http://www.chronocompendium.com/Term/Music_(Chrono_Cross).html | publisher=Chrono Compendium | accessdate=2006-07-24 | archive-date=2006-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060705222749/http://www.chronocompendium.com/Term/Music_%28Chrono_Cross%29.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《盗不走的宝石》因被视作平行次元，而排出在系列主线之外<ref name="radicalcontinuity">'''Kid:''' Radical Dreamers...!? And me name's on here, too! What the bloody hell is goin' on? ... / '''Kid:''' ......This seems to be an archive from a different time than our own. Aside from the two worlds we already know about...there may be other worlds and times which exist... {{cite video game | title =Chrono Cross | developer =Square Co | publisher =Square EA | date=2000-08-15 | platform =PlayStation }}</ref>。《穿越时空》出货達150万套并获得大多數媒体的称赞<ref name="square-sales" /><ref name="gamerankings-cross">{{cite web | title=Game Rankings: Chrono Cross | url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages4/196917.asp | publisher=[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]] | accessdate=2007-07-27 | archive-date=2007-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071020052718/http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages4/196917.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="tomato-cross">{{cite web | title=Rotten Tomatoes: Chrono Cross | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/g/playstation/chrono_cross/ | publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=2007-07-27 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070320044123/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/g/playstation/chrono_cross/ | archivedate=2007-03-20 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

虽然坂口博信在2001年称《穿越时空》开发者想要制作一款新时空游戏<ref name="chrono3discussion">{{cite web | author=Shahed Ahmed | date=2001-07-03 | title=New Chrono game in planning stages | url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/2782608.html?q=chrono | publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | accessdate=2006-07-01 | archive-date=2012-01-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118221013/http://www.gamespot.com/news/2782608.html?q=chrono | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但并没有制作新作的计划。同年史克威尔在日本和美国分别申请商标“[[Chrono_Brake|Chrono Brake]]”和“Chrono Break”。然而美国的商标在2003年被放弃<ref name="sadtrademark">{{cite web | date=2003-11-13 | title=Latest Status Info | url=http://tarr.uspto.gov/servlet/tarr?regser=serial&entry=76345716 | publisher=Trademark Applications and Registration Retrieval | accessdate=2006-07-01 | archive-date=2005-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051123102906/http://tarr.uspto.gov/servlet/tarr?regser=serial&entry=76345716 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。总监时田贵司在2003年的采访中提到了“时空之轮2”<ref name="tokita">{{cite web | date=2003-07-16 | title=【ゲームな人々】第11回 長きに渡って活躍する凄腕プロデューサー　時田貴司氏(後編) | url=http://game.goo.ne.jp/contents/news/NGN20030716exp03/index.html | accessdate=2008-01-15 | publisher=game.goo.ne.jp | language=ja | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060307204754/http://game.goo.ne.jp/contents/news/NGN20030716exp03/index.html | archivedate=2006-03-07 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。堀井雄二在2005年表示他无意继续制作时空系列<ref name="horii1up">{{cite web | author=Alex Fraioli, Sam Kennedy | date=2005-12-02 | title=Dragon Quest vs. America | url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=1&cId=3146024 | publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | accessdate=2007-10-01 | archive-date=2007-09-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927193154/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=1&cId=3146024 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而坂口博信在2007年4月称他创作的《[[蓝龙|蓝龙]]》是《时空之轮》的“延展”<ref name="bluedragon">{{Cite journal |date=June 2007 | volume=216 | pages= 53 |journal=[[Electronic_Gaming_Monthly|Electronic Gaming Monthly]] | publisher=Ziff Davis Publishing Holdings Inc.}}</ref>。光田康典表示有兴趣为新游戏配乐，但担心系列会“会涉及太多的政治”。他强调加藤正人应该参与开发<ref name="mitsuda2008">{{cite web | first=Sam | last=Kennedy | date=2008-01-28 | title=Radical Dreamer: Yasunori Mitsuda Interview from 1UP.com | url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=0&cId=3162780 | publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | accessdate=2008-02-08 | archive-date=2012-12-05 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20121205003225/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=0&cId=3162780 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年2月的《Game Informer》将《时空之轮》列为“十大最期待续作”的第8名，称游戏“是史克威尔产品目录的坚实遗产”，并问道“什么该死的搁延？！”<ref name="gameinformer">{{Cite journal |date=February 2008 | author=Game Informer staff | journal=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | pages= 24–25 | publisher=GameStop Corporation}}</ref>在《电子游戏月刊》的2008年6月“怀旧刊”中，编辑·杰里米·帕里什称时空系列是电子游戏爱好者最渴望看到续作的系列<ref name="egmretro">{{Cite journal |date=June 2008 | first=Jeremy |last=Parish | journal=[[Electronic_Gaming_Monthly|Electronic Gaming Monthly]] |title=Retro Issue: Missing in Action |pages= 95 | publisher=Ziff Davis Inc.}}</ref>。在《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》2009年5月的第一刊中，《时空之轮》在读者最渴望续作投票的50款游戏中名列14<ref name="famitsu14">{{Cite journal | date=May 2009 | journal=ファミ通 | title=Famitsu Readers Vote Their Most Wanted Sequels | url=http://www.ps3hyper.com/news/famitsu-readers-voted-their-most-wanted-sequels/ | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090504023116/http://www.ps3hyper.com/news/famitsu-readers-voted-their-most-wanted-sequels/ | archivedate=2009-05-04 | author= | access-date=2014-08-03 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]] 2009上，史克威尔艾尼克斯高级副总裁[[桥本真司|桥本真司]]称“如果人们想要续作就应该多去购买！”<ref name="sevp">{{cite web | first=Alex | last=Donaldson | date=2009-06-05 | title=Square: Want more Chrono Trigger? Buy More! | url=http://wayback.archive.org/web/20120612201144/http://www.rpgsite.net/news/342-square-want-more-chrono-trigger-buy-more | accessdate=2009-06-15 | archive-date=2012-06-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120612201144/http://www.rpgsite.net/news/342-square-want-more-chrono-trigger-buy-more }}</ref>

在2010年7月对[[费格斯·厄克特|费格斯·厄克特]]的一次采访中，当问到他最想参与什么系列创作时，他答道“如果可以在所有玩过的游戏中”，他会选择《时空之轮》游戏。当时厄克特的公司[[黑曜石娱乐|黑曜石娱乐]]正在为史克威尔艾尼克斯制作《[[末日危城III|末日危城III]]》。厄克特称，“你制作RPG，我们制作RPG，能看到我们合作就太好了。而且他们真的想开始设涉足西式RPG。那么，稍微让它最终结合起来。”<ref>{{cite web| title=Square: Obsidian Would Like To Work On Chrono Trigger| url=http://www.siliconera.com/2010/07/06/obsidian-would-like-to-work-on-chrono-trigger/| accessdate=2010-07-16| archive-date=2010-07-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100711143200/http://www.siliconera.com/2010/07/06/obsidian-would-like-to-work-on-chrono-trigger/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title=Square: Obsidian wants to make Chrono Trigger| url=http://www.destructoid.com/obsidian-wants-to-make-chrono-trigger-178305.phtml| accessdate=2010-07-16| archive-date=2010-07-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100709015726/http://www.destructoid.com/obsidian-wants-to-make-chrono-trigger-178305.phtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>北濑佳范在2011年称他以《时空之轮》的时间旅行机制作为《[[最终幻想XIII-2|最终幻想XIII-2]]》的出发点<ref name="kitaseffxiii2">{{cite web | title=Final Fantasy XIII-2: remaking FF7, Kinect RPGs and killing the "girly" feel | url=http://www.oxm.co.uk/36521/interviews/final-fantasy-xiii-2-remaking-ff7-kinect-rpgs-and-killing-the-girly-feel/?page=3 | accessdate=2013-04-21 | date=November 2011 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102122314/http://www.oxm.co.uk/36521/interviews/final-fantasy-xiii-2-remaking-ff7-kinect-rpgs-and-killing-the-girly-feel/?page=3 | archive-date=2012-01-02 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

